Katie Schoepfer scored a goal with six seconds remaining to lift the Penn State womens soccer team past Minnesota PERIOD

The Nittany Lions   Big Ten beat the Big Ten coleader by a  score to run their winning streak to four games PERIOD

Schoepfers goal came off a set piece  yards out after Minnesota was whistled for a foul PERIOD It was the seniors sixth goal of the year PERIOD

The Lions were kept in the game by senior goalkeeper Alyssa Naeher who made  saves while pushing her shutout streak to  minutes PERIOD Overall Penn State recorded  shots with  on goal PERIOD
